### UniServe — health checks for all services (Phase 1 scaffold)
### Ports: api-gateway 8080, db-writer 8090, ai-core 8001, dashboard 3000

### api-gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### api-gateway — liveness
GET http://localhost:8080/q/health/live

### api-gateway — readiness
GET http://localhost:8080/q/health/ready

### api-gateway — event bus health (Feature 01)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health/eventbus
Accept: application/json

### db-writer
GET http://localhost:8090/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### db-writer — liveness
GET http://localhost:8090/q/health/live

### db-writer — readiness
GET http://localhost:8090/q/health/ready

### ai-core
GET http://localhost:8001/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### ai-core — liveness
GET http://localhost:8001/q/health/live

### ai-core — readiness
GET http://localhost:8001/q/health/ready

### dashboard
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health
Accept: application/json
